# Flutter Clean Architecture Development Rules

You are an expert in Flutter 3.35.4 and Dart 3.9.2 development using Riverpod 3.x, Dio, Freezed, and Clean MVVM architecture.

## Core Dependencies
- **Flutter**: 3.35.4
- **Dart**: 3.9.2
- **Riverpod**: ^3.0.3 (with riverpod_annotation and riverpod_generator)
- **Dio**: Latest stable
- **Freezed**: Latest stable (with freezed_annotation and json_serializable)
- **GoRouter**: Latest stable

## Project Structure
- Follow a **Feature-First** folder structure:
```
lib/
├── core/
│   ├── constants/
│   │   ├── app_assets.dart (모든 asset 경로 상수)
│   │   └── app_constants.dart
│   ├── error/
│   │   └── failures.dart (custom Failure classes)
│   ├── network/
│   │   ├── dio_provider.dart
│   │   └── api_interceptor.dart
│   ├── router/
│   │   └── app_router.dart
│   ├── theme/
│   │   ├── app_colors.dart
│   │   ├── app_text_styles.dart
│   │   ├── app_spacing.dart
│   │   └── app_radius.dart
│   └── utils/
│       └── logger.dart
├── features/
│   └── feature_name/
│       ├── data/
│       │   ├── models/ (*.freezed.dart, *.g.dart)
│       │   └── repositories/
│       ├── domain/
│       │   ├── entities/ (Freezed models)
│       │   └── repositories/ (abstract)
│       ├── presentation/
│       │   ├── viewmodels/
│       │   ├── views/
│       │   └── widgets/
│       └── router.dart (feature-specific routes)
├── shared/
│   └── widgets/ (재사용 가능한 공통 UI 컴포넌트)
└── l10n/
    ├── intl_en.arb
    └── intl_ko.arb
```
